You can use the [`find()` method][1] on your array. Here&#39;s an example:
&lt;!-- begin snippet: js hide: false console: true babel: false --&gt;

&lt;!-- language: lang-js --&gt;

    var items = [
      &#39;https://myfirebaseapp.com/videos/nice.mp4&#39;,
